{"tid":840774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【分裂國家】瑞典節目主持：道歉僅限中國民眾而不是中國政府。","createTime":"2018-09-29T05:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T12:19:47.000Z","uid":3822,"like":88,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8ddffda3dbd18f9fde9a0ee2cf72025db15b0509","tid":840774,"uid":3822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/132139_cb8cdcedcf23a036c8339f8b7e22d002.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F132139_cb8cdcedcf23a036c8339f8b7e22d002.png&h=288063a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n瑞典電視台SVT節目被指「辱華」事件，似乎沒完沒了。涉事的節目主持人羅恩達爾（Jesper R&ouml;nndahl），昨晚在最新一輯的節目中作出道歉，但他強調道欺僅限向感到受冒犯的中國民眾而非中國政府，同時指摘中國政不尊重言論自由。中國駐瑞典大使館發言人隨後表示，不接受羅恩達爾所為，並指堅決反對用心險惡的「道歉」。<br />\n<br />\n據內地媒體報道，羅恩達爾在節目開始後，首先自嘲遭遇網絡暴力，稱自己要違反「諷刺的憲法」，為一個玩笑道歉，因為這個玩笑讓10多億人難受，肯定不是好玩笑。不過，羅恩達爾在向「所有感到被種族主義傷害的人道歉」之後強調，這個道歉僅限對民眾而不對中國政府，他同時指摘中國政府不尊重言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n至於節目使用了錯誤的中國地圖問題，羅恩達爾並沒有道歉，還合成了一幅五星紅旗覆蓋全世界的地圖，並說自己收到了一封瑞典地圖，缺少哥特蘭島的部份，他也要抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國駐瑞典大使館發言人透過《人民日報》發表公開聲明直斥，該節目組從拒絕道歉，到「向感到被冒犯的個人道歉」，再到「向在中國和瑞典的感到被傷害的個人道歉」。這些「道歉」都是極不嚴肅、極不真誠的，「始終迴避種族主義的本質，始終迴避排華辱華的本質，始終迴避傷害中國民族感情和國家尊嚴的本質。現在又惡毒攻擊中國政府，妄圖把中國人民和中國政府對立起來，用心極其險惡。」<br />\n<br />\n聲明又謂：「任何把中國政府和人民對立起來的企圖都是徒勞的。我們堅決反對這種用心險惡的『道歉』。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd02e92adc9c0e17e97fc5830ae6d2fbcbd9fae2","tid":840774,"uid":37220,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:25:03.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff3db5396c5645cf6912b0c408a2ec3d4bc1698","tid":840774,"uid":22736,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:26:23.000Z","msg":"比人串多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f9ec4a3b182d194cdd211f9dcf11851f9b06a7","tid":840774,"uid":77196,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:26:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">首先自嘲遭遇網絡暴力</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班白痴帝吧狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576c8d5fd17b2418f39b2e9d9e86eb493240bcc7","tid":840774,"uid":45232,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:27:49.000Z","msg":"張地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983743e9b43a0da6ac6d2ce2f08372579e3c542a","tid":840774,"uid":61279,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:27:55.000Z","msg":"撚狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff9656cf6fd74ef1d23753d98deec0ffdb6a1d4","tid":840774,"uid":61279,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"576c8d5fd17b2418f39b2e9d9e86eb493240bcc7","tid":840774,"uid":45232,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:27:49.000Z","msg":"張地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:28:33.000Z","msg":"笑什麼，全世界都是支那人.jpg"},{"pid":"db601cfdb7085e9a2c793cca0a0455ddbb522e8e","tid":840774,"uid":182499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:29:31.000Z","msg":"地球是中國的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7d316113ea3e78fd54a6ec5fa6824be51dda55","tid":840774,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"db601cfdb7085e9a2c793cca0a0455ddbb522e8e","tid":840774,"uid":182499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:29:31.000Z","msg":"地球是中國的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:30:36.000Z","msg":"笑到仆街"},{"pid":"dfbccae24a437c53454f1bae2c914158a025d2ef","tid":840774,"uid":11148,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:32:10.000Z","msg":"又撚狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5de4c1d483c76d7c574ef98eb6737e35648370","tid":840774,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:32:31.000Z","msg":"笑話：外抗宜家，內愛宜家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cb9ed6bdabdd3112e3b35a3ce9716e659b0116","tid":840774,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:34:02.000Z","msg":"支那狗自取其辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68510ca59f18047716a9e2b3410b252b6d05eb52","tid":840774,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"Kina<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5e4f1e45f6292d4fc7a01e392fef49ee6a0df1","tid":840774,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比人串多次&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c56a973fc686d0c88eda5305300f910ecda8d4","tid":840774,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:35:20.000Z","msg":"叫支那同新疆道歉先啦"},{"pid":"6dcd096d689befe3c22332e6a1dbc6f3af69c495","tid":840774,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"576c8d5fd17b2418f39b2e9d9e86eb493240bcc7","tid":840774,"uid":45232,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:27:49.000Z","msg":"張地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:36:43.000Z","msg":"全部俾晒你支那 滿意未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032f950c76a7a63df7b380e80eb11197e52e0734","tid":840774,"uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:39:08.000Z","msg":"中國駐瑞典大使館發言人透過《人民日報》發表公開聲明直斥，該節目組從拒絕道歉，到「向感到被冒犯的個人道歉」，再到「向在中國和瑞典的感到被傷害的個人道歉」。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>這些「道歉」都是極不嚴肅、極不真誠的</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n同支那狙撚住日本道歉一樣，又話唔嚴肅唔真誠又盛。<br />\n總之狙擊到永遠為止。"},{"pid":"6c7bb1cb89903684b5e763908c4e1f5f222117dc","tid":840774,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:39:54.000Z","msg":"「向感到被冒犯的個人道歉」，再到「向在中國和瑞典的感到被傷害的個人道歉」<br />\n<br />\n人哋一直都係向<span style=\"color: red;\">個人</span>道歉，啲共產集體人點會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16763977acf7c8c7c4567ef7a947d2fdcf6063b4","tid":840774,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd02e92adc9c0e17e97fc5830ae6d2fbcbd9fae2","tid":840774,"uid":37220,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:25:03.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db0b88f5b9931b7ab714f96e01dea1d10b2ccaf","tid":840774,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"俾舊骨你食，再一大巴車落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a268244034f126bceaf8f9612a44413fb1d4ac","tid":840774,"uid":22633,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:46:06.000Z","msg":"其實鬼佬識玩嘅可以將容易引發支那玻璃心嘅新聞同支那禁忌結合，<br />\n例如呢條片加入好多天津爆炸，高鐵事故政府隱瞞真相處理手段，<br />\n等班愛國憤青係咁轉，然後五毛打手又係咁打護航，微博又係咁刪，<br />\n睇佢地鬼打鬼，<br />\n撚狗撚到化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb169acd3720983a9b62766c99f4af41a598c0df","tid":840774,"uid":3822,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"6dcd096d689befe3c22332e6a1dbc6f3af69c495","tid":840774,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"576c8d5fd17b2418f39b2e9d9e86eb493240bcc7","tid":840774,"uid":45232,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:27:49.000Z","msg":"張地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:36:43.000Z","msg":"全部俾晒你支那 滿意未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"宇宙自古以來都是中國的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/134605_012007d4ae230ed68b319aef1e271f72.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F134605_012007d4ae230ed68b319aef1e271f72.png&h=5fe3d720&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64905930a71ed5df5222010bd63820af2b145075","tid":840774,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfefc28498849ff0691985f32dd9b3d478c0f9f","tid":840774,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:50:46.000Z","msg":"道歉就已經係輸左, 已經係柒頭"},{"pid":"fa51f2fa2fc44cb32a374c03e72ca241a37f1483","tid":840774,"uid":161222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T06:42:11.000Z","msg":"上面話道歉就係認輸個Ｄ真係笑死人<br />\n<br />\n瑞典依場戲碼高招，撚到你一仆一碌。<br />\n<br />\n根據內容，林格倫坦承SVT犯了3個錯誤。<span style=\"color: red;\">一是項目組對「中華民族的文化習俗缺少起碼的了解」</span>；二是「技術處理錯誤」，節目的目標觀眾是「瑞典本土成人群體，不是針對瑞典以外觀眾，更不是針對華人群體」；三是「沒有正確處理好觀眾的批評反應」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瑞典要妥協大可以話係針對遊客個人行為。依家特登講到明係民族文化，話曬俾全世界都知你係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[img][/img]"}]}